@base = http://localhost:5190
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### ============================================
### CARD MANAGEMENT API TESTS
### ============================================

### 1. Get All Cards
GET {{base}}/api/card
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Get Specific Card
GET {{base}}/api/card/{card-id}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Get Cards for Account
GET {{base}}/api/card/account/{account-id}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Create New Card
POST {{base}}/api/card
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cardNumber": "4532015112830366",
  "cardName": "My Visa Card",
  "expirationDate": "2027-12-31T00:00:00Z",
  "cvc": "123",
  "accountId": "your-account-id-here"
}

###

### 5. Update Card (Change Status)
PUT {{base}}/api/card/{card-id}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cardName": "Updated Card Name",
  "status": 2
}

###

### 6. Delete Card
DELETE {{base}}/api/card/{card-id}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ============================================
### NOTES:
### - {card-id}: Replace with valid card GUID
### - {account-id}: Replace with valid account GUID
### - {{token}}: Enter JWT token
### - CardStatus Enum Values:
###   0 = None
###   1 = WaitingForApproval
###   2 = Active
###   3 = Blocked
###   4 = Expired
### ============================================
